Package edu.uw.tcss450.group8.frolicker.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EventAdapter
    The EventAdapter takes event data from Event objects and puts it into a View
    EventCard
    The EventCard class holds all the data for an event
    EventSearchService
    The EventSearchService class is an AsyncTask for searching for events.
    PrefList
    This class stores the user's preferences, and information on the user.
    PrefsInitAdapter
    This is the adapter class used to display initial preferences as a RecyclerView
    PrefsInitAdapter.Holder
    Internal class that represents one item in the RecyclerView
